  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162150/extras/ae447b95bcac5e40ad767feab5b3f900.avif?t=1739637153\" width=600 height=194 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >VR Run</h2><br><i>A Run In Place VR Game</i><br><br>Run into a virtual world just by running in place.<br><br><strong>Two game modes</strong><br>Free run: Where you can run wherever you want.<br>Follow mode: You have to follow your partner.<br><br>You can track the distance and time.<br><br>The first release contains a night city environment. We are planning new environments to be added.<br><br>We are working on new amazing features, so be aware of the future updates.<br><br><strong>You can play VR Run on an Oculus VR headset. We will be working on compatibility for more VR headsets.</strong>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2162150/extras/ae447b95bcac5e40ad767feab5b3f900.avif?t=1739637153\" width=600 height=194 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >VR Run</h2><br><i>A Run In Place VR Game</i><br><br>Run into a virtual world just by running in place.<br><br><strong>Two game modes</strong><br>Free run: Where you can run wherever you want.<br>Follow mode: You have to follow your partner.<br><br>You can track the distance and time.<br><br>The first release contains a night city environment. We are planning new environments to be added.<br><br>We are working on new amazing features, so be aware of the future updates.<br><br><strong>You can play VR Run on an Oculus VR headset. We will be working on compatibility for more VR headsets.</strong>",
